Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and disclose personal information when you use our iOS app GIGit.

Information We Collect

We collect and use the following information:

User email information: We collect your email address only for the purpose of user authentication and to save data inputted by you. We use Firebase Authentication and Firebase Firestore to store and retrieve this information securely.
Ad information: We use Google AdMob to display ads in our App. AdMob may collect certain information, including your device ID, IP address, and location information, to provide relevant ads.
Use of Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide and maintain our App: We use your email address to authenticate your account and to save data inputted by you in Firebase Firestore.
Personalize your experience: We use Google AdMob to display relevant ads to you based on your interests and location.
Improve our App: We use aggregated usage data to analyze and improve the performance of our App.
Disclosure of Information

We may disclose your personal information to third parties in the following circumstances:

Service providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers, such as Firebase and Google AdMob, who perform services on our behalf. These service providers may have access to your information only to the extent necessary to perform their functions.
Legal requirements: We may disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to a lawful request by a government authority.
Security

We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. We use industry-standard security measures, such as encryption and secure data storage, to protect your information.

Your Rights

You have certain rights with respect to your personal information, including the right to access, correct, or delete your information. You may also have the right to object to or restrict our use of your information. To exercise your rights, please contact us at gigitfeedback@gmail.com.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at [insert contact email].
